info.author: Oliver Steele
classifiers: Topic :: Software Development :: Libraries :: Python Modules
info.description:
This package contains functions for manipulating Finite-State Automata (FSAs). 
It includes functions for minimizing and determinizing FSAs, computing FSA
intersections and unions, compiling a (non-POSIX) regular expression into an
FSA, and compiling a set of regular expression productions into a chart parser.
info.name: FSA
